parameters:
\OC[5]Welcome \ANN[1]. It's truly impressive
that you boldly came here alone. You truly are a
remarkable holy knight.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>If that's the case, why don't you show yourself as
well? Let's settle this fair and square.

\CE[79]\OC[5] Yes, of course. However, the area
you are currently in is my experimental field. It
is not suitable for a decisive battle. So, I would
like you to come to the main hall where I am.

\OC[5] However, the disc you are currently on is
actually a transportation device to the main hall.
Unfortunately, I accidentally turned off the
power.

\OC[5] I apologize, but could you please activate
the transportation devices in the four rooms in
that area? By doing so, you will be able to come
to the main hall.

\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────......I thought as much. I didn't think
someone who uses such magic would settle things
properly.

\CE[79]\OC[5]How disappointing. \.Well, I suppose
someone like you, whose mind is soaked in sexual
desire and wearing the skin of a holy person,
wouldn't understand the concept of strategy.

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────......As expected of a demon, your foul mouth
speaks for itself. Your words don't resonate with
me at all.

\CE[79]\OC[5] Anyway, if you're coming, please
quickly activate the power.

\OC[5] By the way, please be careful as my pets
and experimental animal monsters are wandering
around the area.
\OC[5] Well then, I'll be waiting. Hehehe...
エリア別獲得アイテムリスト追加
'Go to the four rooms of the Demon Lords castle and activate the teleportation devices'

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>It seems like all the power has been activated and
the transportation device to the main shrine is
now usable... With this, we can go to Dimon's
place anytime...
'Defeat the Demon in the main hall of the Demon Lords temple'
